      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING COLUMBUS (5) charged out of the boxes with a slick early split and went straight to the front, scoring an all the way win (24.95) over 450m at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. SPARRING (8) flew the lids with a sensational early split and led throughout to score an impressive win by 3.5 lengths over 450m at this track (25.07). Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Expected to measure up again. CALY JET (1) goes very well over this trip including two wins. Comes off a (25.11) win last time, scoring by 1.5 lengths in a Special conditions H over 450m at this track. Looks well placed here and among the chances. PAW WINKWORTH (2) placed last time out so worth considering.",
